text: "These intentionally planned and executed mass school shooting happened since December 2012, the time of the horrific Sandy Hook Elementary shootings leaving 26 six-year-old students and facility dead. They were selected by <a href="http://www.politifact.com/truth-o-meter/statements/2014/jun/13/everytown-gun-safety/have-there-been-74-school-shootings-sandy-hook-clo/" target="_blank" rel="">Politifact.com</a> of Tampa Bay Times, from the <a href="http://everytown.org/article/schoolshootings/" target="_blank" rel="" title="Link: http://everytown.org/article/schoolshootings/">74 school shootings</a> recorded by advocacy group Everytown."
